## Workflow

```
1. /pm          → Create PRD
2. /architect   → Design architecture
3. /sm          → Create stories
4. /dev         → Implement
5. /qa          → Review & gate (PASS/CONCERNS/FAIL)
6. Commit only after QA PASS
```

## Agent Commands

All agents support these commands (use `*` prefix):

- `*help` — Show available commands
- `*load-context` — Load project context
- `*save-context` — Save session
- `*exit` — Leave agent mode

